# Reindex

## Goal
Rebuild the {{config.project.name}} wiki index and verify taxonomy integrity.

<workflow>

<step n="1" goal="Scan all wiki pages">
  <action>Walk the filesystem under `wiki/` and catalog every .md file</action>
  <action>For each page, read frontmatter to extract: type, title, tags, last_updated, source_count</action>
  <action>Build an in-memory catalog of all pages with their metadata</action>
</step>

<step n="2" goal="Categorize pages">
  <action>Group pages by type: entities, concepts, sources, comparisons</action>
  <action>Within each group, sort according to {{config.knowledge.organization}} style:</action>
  <action>entity-first: alphabetical by title | topic-first: by primary tag | chronological: by date | thesis-driven: by confidence level</action>
</step>

<step n="3" goal="Detect naming issues">
  <action>Check for duplicate pages (same entity/concept with different filenames)</action>
  <action>Check for inconsistent naming conventions (mixed case, inconsistent slugification)</action>
{{#if (eq config.workflows.ingestion_style "autonomous")}}
  <action>Automatically resolve naming conflicts using the most descriptive, unambiguous name — update all references to point to the resolved name</action>
  <action>Log each resolution with `[AUTO] reindex-rename | {old name} → {new name} | {reasoning}`</action>
{{else}}
  <action>Flag naming conflicts for the user to resolve</action>
{{/if}}
</step>

<step n="4" goal="Verify cross-references">
  <action>Scan all {{config.wiki.cross_ref_style}} links across the wiki</action>
  <action>Verify every link target exists</action>
  <action>Flag broken links and suggest fixes</action>
</step>

<step n="5" goal="Rebuild index.md">
  <action>Generate a fresh `wiki/index.md` from the catalog</action>
  <action>Include: page count per category, one-line descriptions, {{config.wiki.cross_ref_style}} links</action>
  <action>Add summary statistics at the top: total pages, total sources, last updated date</action>
</step>

<step n="6" goal="Log and report">
  <action>Append a reindex entry to `wiki/log.md` with: pages indexed, issues found, changes made</action>
{{#if (includes config.workflows.tools "qmd")}}
  <action>Run `qmd update` to refresh the search index</action>
{{/if}}
  <action>Report summary: pages indexed, naming issues, broken links, changes to index</action>
</step>

</workflow>
